This is how to double_the_difference of lst:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this lst's length times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      When x is more than 0, then:
         When remainder of x and 2 is 1, then:
            Remember that total is sum of total and (product of x and x)
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
